snippet.title: Petal Crash Online (trailer)
snippet.description:
Petal Crash Online is a free upgrade on Steam for owners of Petal Crash, a game about smashing blocks together and now you can play it competitively.


https://store.steampowered.com/app/1211110/Petal_Crash/
